    <center><table class="itemDisplayTable">
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Title:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">A Study on Analysis of Working Capital Management in Perfect International Fabricators</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Authors:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Ganapathi Raman.G</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Keywords:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Capital Management<br />Perfect International Fabricators</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Issue Date:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">May-2012 </td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Publisher:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">SRM University</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Series/Report no.:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">P5638</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Abstract:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">The present business world is becoming more complex because of its dynamics future .in that case ,the management should be more active and efficient in order to overcome the abstacle,which requires effective financial management ,in order to pinpoint problem,adopt necessary and relevant steps for the smooth running of the company.
A company’s working capital is an important act in the business .The working capital will help the business concern in carrying out its day to day activities .various attempts have been made by the finance managers for effective utilization of the short term funds.The efficient managing of working capital is often studied through a detailed analysis of various ratios calculated on the basis of profitability ,liquid and turnover.
The thesis work entitled ,” A STUDY ON WORKING CAPITAL IN PERFECT INTERNATIONAL COMPANY PVT.LIMITED “was undertaken with the objective of assessing the performance of financial performance i.e.. the existing system inventory and receivables and payables management of the company by analyzing the financial data,with the help of ratio analysis and to offer suggestions for the improvement of the management of financial performance
From the study it can be generally concluded that the companies working capital management has been going on right lines and there has been a close co-operation between finance,technical and other executives and there is commited involvement for producing good result to achieve harmony in the working environs of the company.</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">URI:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue"><a href="http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/9785">http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/9785</a></td></tr>
